  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study was to evaluate the effect of listening to ambient music on the
      perceived exertion rate during pulmonary rehabilitation for chronic obstructive pulmonary
      disease patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
